    "content_zh_hk": "拜登政府壓下了一份舉報投訴，指控福奇在疫情期間就相關問題向國會撒謊：https://justthenews.com/accountability/whistleblowers/biden-administration-buried-whistleblower-complaint-alleging-fauci",
