    "content_zh_hk": "五角大樓稱，特朗普政府將從北約盟友德國撤出數千名駐軍：https://www.breitbart.com/europe/2026/05/02/trump-admin-to-withdraw-thousands-of-troops-from-nato-ally-germany/",
